          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_KHaGbhAo2c5fNyRWJBITirR9Sb94f0vkvosp3JvWEkcYJqifog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I always enjoy my experience at HDA. I\u2019ve been going there for almost 2 decades. Dr. R is excellent and her staff and ambience equally wonderful. However, for the first time yesterday (4/21/26) the dental tech that did my cleaning can use a little training in \u201cbedside\u201d manners. She was stoic and a bit impersonal. This was my first time seeing or interacting (minimal) with her at the office. I\u2019ll update when I learn her name (no introductions made). She could\u2019ve been having a not so good day.  She didn\u2019t ask questions about my teeth status prior to cleaning, and she gave me no update as to how my teeth is doing, and the like. She was dry as it comes. May be she was upset because I was running 15 minutes behind or she\u2019s simply new to the job. I wish her luck.\nThat\u2019s my dental office that I go with my kids so definitely going back and totally recommend.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5MlVHczJaakJtYUVGYWExQlRTWE5sU3pSSFJGRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa92b09d95173d0b9!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOl92UGs2ZjBmaEFaa1BTSXNlSzRHRFE%7C%7C?hl=en",
