        {
          "username": "Kisha Moreira",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "104899145091307627229",
          "user_review_count": 4,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNyu5Es_PbGY0ZnihQR8fEtFD1RAIGV3gL23tN33qhjG6u_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I recently had an outstanding experience at Harlem Dental Associates and felt compelled to share it. From the moment I walked in, the professionalism and warmth of the staff were evident. The reception and administrative team were welcoming and efficient, setting a positive tone for my visit.\n\nJenny, who handled my deep cleaning, was absolutely amazing. Her expertise and gentle approach made the process comfortable and stress-free. I felt relaxed and well taken care of throughout the procedure.\n\nImani was another standout during my visit. Her sweet and attentive nature was reassuring, especially as she took the time to explain everything that would be done during my first visit. Her thoroughness and kindness made a significant difference in my experience.\n\nI also had the pleasure of meeting Dr. Riordan, who was incredibly welcoming and calming. She took the time to go over all my X-rays and addressed any past or future concerns I had from other dental offices. Her thoroughness and willingness to listen made me feel valued and confident in the care I was receiving.\n\nOverall, Harlem Dental Associates exceeded my expectations with their exceptional care and attention to detail. I highly recommend them to anyone seeking a professional and compassionate dental team.",
