          "description": "Harlem Dental Associates is the BEST Dentist in Harlem. I've been coming here with my children over 20 years. I tried other dentists in the area of Spanish and east Harlem and none comes close to quality and care you get there at Harlem Dental Associates. All others I went to just looked to get money from both the insurance and myself, and didn't perform the basics with as much care and treatment. They take most insurance and are very helpful both online and over the phone.  They're the ABSOLUTE BEST.",
